532
00:32:46,330 --> 00:32:48,030
What if...

533
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:51,609
Your Highness, Xu Rugui is a criminal wanted by the imperial court.

534
00:32:51,610 --> 00:32:53,179
Whether he is dead or alive,

535
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:55,590
